#

Buffalo Chicken Nachos

25 min
$10
700 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyWheat (if chips contain gluten)

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

AppetizerSnack

Tags:

SnackParty FoodComfort Food

Description

A spicy and cheesy twist on classic nachos, perfect for game day or a quick snack!

Ingredients

  • tortilla chips: 1 bag
  • cooked chicken, shredded: 2 cups
  • buffalo sauce: 1/2 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 2 cups
  • blue cheese crumbles: 1/2 cup
  • green onions, sliced: 2
  • sour cream: for serving
  • jalapeños, sliced (optional): to taste
